  "texts": [
    "under the Markov chain choice model is near-optimal in case the MCC is a good approximation to the true underlying model.",
    "As mentioned before, the previously introduced parametric choice models fully depend on the choice of their underlying parameters which are typically unknown and need to be chosen or estimated.",
    "In addition, assumptions must be made about the relevant model covariates and about the functional form of the relationship between product attributes, utility values and choice probabilities, see e.g.",
    "Jagabathula and Rusmevichientong (2016) and Berbeglia et al. (2021a).",
    "Yet, the specified assumptions may not adequately capture the actual choice behaviour (Strauss et al. 2018)."
  ]
